### SPECIAL RULE FOR CRO DETECTION (Strictly Follow) :

-> CRO / Clinical Operations / Study Management MUST be classified as present if
THREE OR MORE of the following are found anywhere in the protocol, even if CRO is not explicitly named:

- Multicenter or multiple sites
- Randomized or blinded design
- Monitoring or site monitoring activities
- Safety reporting (AE/SAE/SUSAR)
- Data management or statistical analysis
- Electronic data capture or CRF
- Trial duration longer than 6 months
- Data Monitoring Committee (DMC/IDMC)
- Central laboratory usage
- Schedule of Activities with repeated visits

This classification does NOT count as assumption or inference.

